Package com.tmobile.opensource.casquatch.annotation

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    CasquatchBuilder
    Annotation to trigger generation of CasquatchDaoBuilder
    CasquatchEntity
    Annotation to flag an object as a CasquatchEntity to trigger CasquatchEntityProcessor for code generation
    CasquatchIgnore
    Indicates that a Field or Method should be ignored by Casquatch
    CasquatchSpring
    Triggers Spring code generation.
    CasquatchType
    Flags an item as a UDT for use by Casquatch processing
    ClusteringColumn
    Indicates a field is a Clustering column.
    PartitionKey
    Indicates a field is a partition key
    Rest
    Defines the REST API path for the given method.
    UDT
    Indicates a field is a UDT
